    "\n",
    "## Season Analysis: Upto Match 51\n",
    "\n",
    "This comprehensive notebook provides an in-depth analysis of the Indian Premier League (IPL) 2026 season, covering match data, player performance, venue insights, and predictive patterns. Our analysis encompasses 51 matches with over 11,000 deliveries, revealing fascinating patterns in batting, bowling, and match outcomes.\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Data Loading and Exploration"
