    "---\n",
    "## 4. Toss Analysis: Does Winning the Toss Matter?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Toss impact analysis\n",
    "print(\"=\"*80)\n",
    "print(\"TOSS IMPACT ANALYSIS\")\n",
    "print(\"=\"*80)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Create toss decision vs match result\n",
    "toss_analysis = pd.crosstab(matches['toss_decision'], matches['match_result'], margins=True)\n",
    "print(\"\\nToss Decision vs Match Result:\")\n",
    "print(toss_analysis)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Calculate toss impact\n",
    "toss_win_matches = matches[matches['toss_winner'] == matches['match_winner']]\n",
    "toss_impact = len(toss_win_matches) / len(matches) * 100\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\nToss Winners Who Won Match: {len(toss_win_matches)} out of {len(matches)} matches\")\n",
    "print(f\"Toss Impact on Match Win: {toss_impact:.1f}%\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Decision impact\n",
    "bat_first = matches[matches['toss_decision'] == 'Bat']\n",
    "bat_second = matches[matches['toss_decision'] == 'Bowl']\n",
    "\n",
    "bat_first_wins = len(bat_first[bat_first['match_winner'] == bat_first['team1']])\n",
    "bat_second_wins = len(bat_second[bat_second['match_winner'] == bat_second['team2']])\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\nBatting First Win Rate: {bat_first_wins/len(bat_first)*100:.1f}% ({bat_first_wins}/{len(bat_first)})\")\n",
    "print(f\"Batting Second Win Rate: {bat_second_wins/len(bat_second)*100:.1f}% ({bat_second_wins}/{len(bat_second)})\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Visualization\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(14, 5))\n",
    "\n",
    "# Toss winner vs match winner\n",
    "toss_data = pd.Series({\n",
    "    'Toss Winner\\nAlso Won Match': len(toss_win_matches),\n",
    "    'Toss Winner\\nLost Match': len(matches) - len(toss_win_matches)\n",
    "})\n",
    "\n",
    "colors_toss = ['#3498db', '#e67e22']\n",
    "axes[0].pie(toss_data.values, labels=toss_data.index, autopct='%1.1f%%',\n",
    "            colors=colors_toss, startangle=90)\n",
    "axes[0].set_title('Toss Winner vs Match Winner', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Bat first vs bat second\n",
    "decision_wins = pd.Series({\n",
    "    'Bat First': bat_first_wins,\n",
    "    'Bat Second': bat_second_wins\n",
    "})\n",
    "\n",
    "colors_decision = ['#2ecc71', '#e74c3c']\n",
    "axes[1].pie(decision_wins.values, labels=decision_wins.index, autopct='%1.1f%%',\n",
    "            colors=colors_decision, startangle=90)\n",
    "axes[1].set_title('Batting Order Win Rate', fontsize=12, fontweight='bold')\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.savefig('../visualizations/toss_impact.png', dpi=300, bbox_inches='tight')\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\n✓ Visualization saved: toss_impact.png\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Story: The Toss - Cricket's Coin Flip with Consequence\n",
    "\n",
    "In cricket, the toss has long been debated as a potential game-changer. Our IPL 2026 data provides compelling evidence:\n",
    "\n",
    "**Key Insights:**\n",
    "- **Toss Impact**: The correlation between winning the toss and winning the match is not absolute\n",
    "- **Strategic Decisions**: Both batting first and chasing appear viable strategies in IPL 2026\n",
    "- **Venue-Dependent**: Success likely depends more on pitch conditions and team composition than the toss itself\n",
    "\n",
    "**The Narrative**: While the toss provides the opportunity to choose, the IPL 2026 season demonstrates that execution matters far more than fortune. Teams that adapt to their chosen batting order and handle pressure are the ones emerging victorious."
