   "source": [
    "### Story: The Death Over Drama\n",
    "\n",
    "The death overs (16-20) in T20 cricket are where matches are won and lost. IPL 2026 has produced specialist finishers who thrive under pressure:\n",
    "\n",
    "**Clutch Performers**: These batters have built reputations for staying calm when stakes are highest. In the final overs, when field restrictions are lifted and bowling options are limited, these players are the insurance policies that teams rely on.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Psychological Edge**: Teams with proven death specialists enjoy a psychological advantage in close matches. Opposition bowlers must bowl perfectly; even slight errors get punished.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Match Impact**: Often, the outcome of an IPL match is decided in these final moments. The players in the death specialist list are the difference-makers in high-pressure situations."
   ]
