   "source": [
    "### Story: Identifying the Match-Winners\n",
    "\n",
    "The Impact Score is a composite metric that synthesizes three critical dimensions of batting:\n",
    "\n",
    "**Strike Rate (40%)**: How quickly can the player score? In T20, aggression and quick scoring are paramount. Higher strike rates put immediate pressure on bowling.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Average (30%)**: How consistent is the player? Average measures longevity in the crease and the player's contribution to overall team performance.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Boundary Percentage (30%)**: How explosive is the player? Boundaries change match momentum and accumulate runs quickly.\n",
    "\n",
    "**The Top Performers** combine all three dimensions—they score quickly (high SR), consistently (high average), and explosively (high boundary%). These are the irreplaceable match-winners that franchises build their strategies around.\n",
    "\n",
    "The players at the top of the Impact Score list are the MVPs of IPL 2026, making them essential to their team's championship aspirations."
